headline: GoDaddy Survey Shows Customer Patience Is Thinning, Unless You're Under 30
summary: Nearly half of U.S. shoppers say customer service provided by businesses is getting worse, according to results from the latest GoDaddy (NYSE: GDDY) Consumer Pulse* survey – yet Gen Z and Millennials remain more upbeat than their parents' generations.
